<http://data.quality-link.eu/ontology/v1#LearningOpportunitySpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The asbtract specification of an opportunity to acquire a given set of learning outcomes, e.g. the general specification of a course, programme or module offered by an education provider.\n\nThis class and its shape are based on the ELM *LearningAchievementSpecificationShape* and *QualificationShape*.\n\nDifferent from the ELM LOQ profile, the shapes are defined as open. Properties that are not used/interpreted by the QualityLink data aggregator have been omitted to simplify the shapes."@en .
